Free Heroes2 Engine

Prerequisites:

You need to have these libraries (with equivalent devel versions) to build fHeroes2:

- libSDL
- libSDLmm

SDL libraries can be found at http://www.libsdl.org . libSDLmm can be found at http://sourceforge.net/projects/sdlmm/ .

Sourcecode: you can get it here: http://sourceforge.net/projects/fheroes2/

win32:
- unpack win32/cygwin/SDL-1.2.11.tgz in to cygwin directory
- unpack win32/cygwin/SDL-0.1.8.tgz in to cygwin directory
- make -f makefile.win32
